{"tid":2303931,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"司法機構：就有《立場新聞》的錯誤引述作出澄清","createTime":"2020-11-28T10:39:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T11:34:30.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a1f2fcc77932e09a41a9db254999b5cc2351652e","tid":2303931,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:39:39.000Z","msg":"司法機構就有網媒一篇報道的錯誤引述，作出澄清；指《立場新聞》星期四引用《金融時報》報道，指稱終審法院首席法官馬道立談及港區國安法的引述，屬於失實錯誤，強調馬道立並無談及或評論國安法，亦無談及國安法對基本法相關條文或法官任命的影響。 <br />\n<br />\n對於《金融時報》原文中引述馬道立指，與中國大陸不同，基本法奠定了本港三權分立的依據，司法機構指，馬道立在2014年法律年度開啟典禮的演辭中，作出有關言論時，講述的是基本法下的司法獨立，演辭並無談及內地的情況。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2368409\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2368409&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CpnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=e80ac9fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2368409</a>"},{"pid":"cfc8d5e7e28a24b4b1c8d88ac4a1998d31708170","tid":2303931,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"有講都可以當無講<br />\n乜個屍法機構連歷史都改變到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ff3f07023c69adce232038c3f8a16ff3a0231cc","tid":2303931,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ATZFo3F.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FATZFo3F.gif&h=19fa77b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45942ef487118f03f9836ce590d0690591d499a5","tid":2303931,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:43:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3590592176b4985c4102be82430921086e1dceac","tid":2303931,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T10:45:43.000Z","msg":"抄埋晒啲外國fake news<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/